data.description: **Motivated Seller!** Charming 4/2 in Oakland Terrace that is convenient to St. Andrews, historic downtown and minutes to the beaches and shopping.  Completely renovated after Hurricane Michael to include a new roof, AC, kitchen cabinets/granite countertops, new flooring and more.  Enjoy the fabulous and spacious fenced back yard year round. There is even enough room for a pool! A new, large shed for storage comes complete with hurricane clips in the roof.  The large screened in porch is perfect for entertaining or quiet evenings.  There is a termite bond that transfers.  **Washer and dryer do not convey. The freezer and both extra refrigerators do not convey.**Insurance is $1400/year. Policy is with Goosehead-Paul Wunstell.
